usign tool:
  1. This tool is copy from openwrt 15.5 built-root. Location:openwrt/staging_dir/host/bin 
  2. Generate keys: ./usign -G -c baiyatech.com -p opkg-SHS-project.pub -s opkg-SHS-project.key 
  3. Sign: ./usign -S -m README -P opkg-SHS-project.key
  4. Verify: ./usign -V -p ./opkg-SHS-project.pub -P . -m README -x ./README.sig 
